
	Furseal is a free opensource,crossing platform 3d game engine.
	This idea originated from Catcake.Furseal the expansion of Catcake.
	Furseal support Chinese document(need Doxygen tool to to extract from sources).
	
	platforms for now:
	
	Android (NDK5, android1.6 or more highter version)
	Linux   (GCC4.4, Ubuntu, Fedora and so on)
	Windows (vs2008, windows Xp, windows Vista, Windows 7 and so on)
	*iPhone
	*MacOSX
	
	Furseal plan:
	
	Polygon and 3D points rendering
  Resource management
  Multi-task management
  Memory management
  Automatic frame-rate adjustment
  Font rendering (TTF, TTC, OTF, and so on)
  Screen splitting
  Lighting (parallel and point lights)
  Input device (mouse and keyboard) management
  *Sound playing
  *Collision detection (sphere, box, triangle and ray)
  *Physical system
  *Configuration file parser
  *2D effects drawing
  *3D model drawing (3DS)
  *Motion playing (Skeletal animation)

